name: Pump It Up
comments: The Wildhearts made an earlier recording of Pump It Up (April 23, 1993) during a session for radio broadcast on The Friday Rock Show, BBC Radio 1, UK.  The earlier (more conventional) recording was later released on "Anarchic Airwaves - The Wildhearts at the BBC" (Kuro Neko, KNEK 3) on March 16, 1998.  The version listed here, although a later recording (in the production style of Endless, Nameless), was the first to be released.
